<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 8 (Xinhua) -- The departments of the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (SAR) government were honored here
Wednesday with the annual Ombudsman Awards from the SAR Office of
The Ombudsman.
</P>
