<HEADLINE> Human Resource Investment Urged in Zimbabwe </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, July 8 (Xinhua) -- There is need for continued
investment in human resources if Zimbabwe is to achieve
sustainable socio-economic development, a cabinet minister said
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
