named his starting line-up in the match against France, the same one
he used in defeating Germany in quarter-finals.
</P>
<P>
Blazevic's decision is reasonable as the team beat Germany so
convincingly.
</P>
<P>
But that means there is still no place for Robert Prosincki.
</P>
