</P>
<P>
Drazen ladc, Igor Stimac, Slaven Bilic, Dario Simic, Robert
Jarni, Zvonimir Soldo, Aljosa Asanovic, Zvonimir Boban, Mario
Stanic, Davor Suker, Silvio maric. 
