<HEADLINE> Kuala Lumpur Stocks Close Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed lower Wednesday with some players
staying on the sidelines in the absence of fresh leads and the
continuing weak market sentiment.
</P>
<P>
