189.874 million ringgit (45.642 million dollars) from Tuesday's
84.946 million valued at 189.675 million ringgit (45.594 million
dollars).
</P>
<P>
Turnover on the second board stood at 4.188 million shares
valued at 5.934 million ringgit (1.426 million dollars) from 4.967
million shares valued at 6.627 million ringgit (1.593 million
dollars) on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Off-market turnover was at 45.903 million shares worth 273.361
million ringgit (65.711 million dollars) from Tuesday's 1.801
million shares valued at 4.788 million ringgit (1.15 million
dollars).
